### ğŸ”¥ **Secret Sauce Algorithm**

Base:  "Hiking" + "7" + "CA"  
       â”‚         â”‚      â””â”€ Location abbreviation  
       â”‚         â””â”€ Lucky digit  
       â””â”€ Hobby  
       
Process:
1. Capitalize("hik") â†’ "Hik"
2. Leet-speak vowels â†’ "H1k"
3. Add separator â†’ "H1k_"
4. Append salted hash â†’ "H1k_7CA!9"
